Odoo Cancel Delivery

Easily cancel delivery orders in odoo and get all your stock return in the warehouse via a single click, cancel multiple delivery orders.

Easy Interface to cancel processed delivery/shipment.
One click to cancel all your inventory transactions.
Mass cancel delivery/shipment.

Finally you can see that your delivery/shipment is cancelled.

In done picking you can see the cancel button, it will reverse all your inventory and cancel that picking.

In setting >> Users >> Access rights, give access Allow Cancel Picking

Open any delivery/shipment which is processed or done.

To cancel multiple delivery/shipments cancel you can go to the list view and select the option "Cancel Picking" as mentioned in the screenshot.
